{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 welcome to mccrabney's repo\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 here you will find some scripts that i have created to fulfill some needs i had in REAPER.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 most of these allow better keyboard/midi controller control of Razor Editss. use these to navigate your project with REs, or to quickly slice/repattern RE blocks. this is great for grid-based sampling and sound design.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 i like to assign these to my directional keys (and all of their modifiers). this lets me navigate my project quickly by grid (keyboard zooming shortcuts are also helpful here)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 note that quickly retriggering scripts that move cursor/RE forwards/backwards will trigger the [ReaScript task control "Script name" is running in the background] message. for each action, select "new instance" and "remember choice" this will retrigger the script and it should behave as expected when hammering a directional key.\par}
